    "Commentary Vol. 83": "For all the wells which his father\u2019s servants had digged, in the days of Abraham `[char_Abraham_Exo_17]` his father, etc.] For the watering of his flocks and herds, [v_Gen_21_25] (see <012125>Genesis 21:25): the Philistines had stopped them, and filled them with earth; that they might be of no use; and this they did through envy to him, and is mentioned as a proof of it.\nVer."
